In this paper, we conduct a systematic analysis of LMs for KBC, where we focus on high precision ranges (90%). We evaluate by first using a new benchmark dataset \ourdataset{}, where we randomly sample facts from Wikidata (including many without any structured information, Wikipedia information, or English labels) and second by a manual evaluation on subject-relation pairs without object values, yet.